_sText:
This map is a castle/for where the terrorists have to take over just by wiping out the other team it features a big metal gate which opens when touched 4 towers which use trigger_push to get you up there and once your up there you can't get down but there is a buyzone on each of the towers, there is a central building which also uses trigger_push to get you up there but this area does not have a buyzone.

it's a fun map to play on if you have any suggestion then leave a message.
